
WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Hi, my name is Nazifa Ahmed.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:06.000
I'm currently a graduate student at the
University of Missouri in the Learning

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Technologies program.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:13.000
I have done my undergrad in childhood
education, and I hope to use both of my

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:18.000
experiences to help me grow my career in
the instructional design field.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.000
With this website,
I want to create an online portfolio

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.000
where I showcase all the skills that I
have worked on in the courses from this

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:29.000
program.
